  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Orality disorders are frequent in child. There are complications like growth and psychomotor
      development disorders.

      The aim is to estimate the prevalence of orality disorder for child with one or several food
      allergy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
